ock-channel"],"comment_count":0,"content":"<p>1、苹果公司料将如期发布iPhone 16。</p>\n\n<p>2、新款iPhone的款式和型号，是否配置A18/A18 Pro芯片。</p>\n\n<p>3、是否提供苹果AI（Apple Intelligence）功能。</p>\n\n<p>4、Apple Watch Series 10和AirPods。</p>\n","content_more":"<p>见闻美股注：</p>\n\n<p>9月9日美东时间13:00（北京时间10日01:00），苹果公司将举办名为“高光时刻”（glowtime）的秋季新品发布会。</p>\n","content_text":"1、苹果公司料将如期发布iPhone 16。\n\n2、新款iPhone的款式和型号，是否配置A18/A18 Pro芯片。\n\n3、是否提供苹果AI（Apple Intelligence）功能。\n\n4、Apple Watch Series 10和AirPods。","cover_images":[],"display_time":1725890340,"fund_codes":[],"global_channel_name":"7x24快讯","global_more_uri":"wscn://wallstreetcn.com/live","has_live_reading":false,"highlight_title":"","id":2784292,"images":[],"is_calendar":false,"is_favourite":false,"is_priced":false,"is_scaling":false,"reference":"","related_themes":[],"score":2,"symbols":[],"tags":[],"title":"苹果2024年秋季新品发布会关注点","type":"live","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/livenews/2784292"},{"article":null,"author":{"avatar":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/ivanka_avatar_5.png","display_name":"葛冬瑾","id":120000004519,"is_followed":false,"uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/authors/120000004519"},"ban_comment":false,"channels":["global-channel","bond-channel"],"comment_count":0,"content":"<p>据中央纪委国家监委网站，江西省纪委监委消息：经中共江西省委批准，江西省纪委监委对江西省金融控股集团有限公司原党委副书记、副董事长、总经理甘成久严重违纪违法问题进行了立案审查调查。</p>\n","content_more":"<p>经查，甘成久身为国有企业党员领导干部，丧失理想信念，背弃初心使命，违反政治纪律，私自携带反动书籍入境并阅看，对抗组织审查；违反中央八项规定精神，接受可能影响公正执行公务的宴请和旅游安排；违反组织原则，在组织函询时不如实说明问题，隐瞒不报个人有关事项，在干部职工录用及职务晋升中，利用职权为他人谋利；廉洁底线失守，接受可能影响公正执行公务的礼品礼金；道德败坏，追求低级趣味；“靠金融吃金融”，利用职权为他人在不良资产收购、项目融资等方面谋取利益，非法收受巨额财物；公器私用、擅权妄为，给国家利益造成巨大损失。</p>\n\n<p>甘成久严重违反党的政治纪律、组织纪律、廉洁纪律、工作纪律、生活纪律和国家法律法规，构成严重职务违法并涉嫌受贿、挪用公款、国有公司人员滥用职权犯罪，且在党的十八大后仍不收敛、不收手，性质严重，影响恶劣，应予严肃处理。依据《中国共产党纪律处分条例》《中华人民共和国监察法》《中华人民共和国公职人员政务处分法》等相关规定，经江西省纪委常委会会议研究并报中共江西省委批准，决定给予甘成久开除党籍处分；由江西省监委给予其开除公职处分；将其涉嫌犯罪问题移送检察机关依法审查起诉，所涉财物一并移送。</p>\n","content_text":"据中央纪委国家监委网站，江西省纪委监委消息：经中共江西省委批准，江西省纪委监委对江西省金融控股集团有限公司原党委副书记、副董事长、总经理甘成久严重违纪违法问题进行了立案审查调查。","cover_images":[],"display_time":1725889651,"fund_codes":[],"global_channel_name":"7x24快讯","global_more_uri":"wscn://wallstreetcn.com/live","has_live_reading":false,"highlight_title":"","id":2784289,"images":[],"is_calendar":false,"is_favourite":false,"is_priced":false,"is_scaling":false,"reference":"","related_themes":[],"score":1,"symbols":[],"tags":[],"title":"江西省金融控股集团有限公司原副董事长、总经理甘成久被“双开”","type":"live","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/livenews/2784289"},{"article":null,"author":{"avatar":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/ivanka_avatar_5.png","display_name":"葛冬瑾","id":120000004519,"is_followed":false,"uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/authors/120000004519"},"ban_comment":false,"channels":["global-channel","us-stock-channel"],"comment_count":0,"content":"<p>美股盘初，主要行业ETF多数走高，半导体ETF、科技行业ETF、全球科技股指数ETF涨幅居前。</p>\n","content_more":"","content_text":"美股盘初，主要行业ETF多数走高，半导体ETF、科技行业ETF、全球科技股指数ETF涨幅居前。","cover_images":[{"uri":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/389742ac-71e6-4e9d-a183-06b5435397dc.png","height":550,"width":419,"size":43299}],"display_time":1725889284,"fund_codes":[],"global_channel_name":"7x24快讯","global_more_uri":"wscn://wallstreetcn.com/live","has_live_reading":false,"highlight_title":"","id":2784288,"images":[{"uri":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/389742ac-71e6-4e9d-a183-06b5435397dc.png","height":550,"width":419,"size":43299}],"is_calendar":false,"is_favourite":false,"is_priced":false,"is_scaling":false,"reference":"","related_themes":[],"score":1,"symbols":[],"tags":[],"title":"","type":"live","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/livenews/2784288"},{"article":{"id":3727383,"image":{"uri":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/b4e3b3bd-4149-49cc-b1a4-b1cc08f36b40.jpeg","height":577,"width":1024,"size":138199},"platforms":["wscn-platform"],"title":"欧美股市强势反弹，纳指盘初涨逾1%，美元兑日元涨1%，铁矿石跌破90美元大关","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3727383"},"author":{"avatar":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/ivanka_avatar_5.png","display_name":"葛冬瑾","id":120000004519,"is_followed":false,"uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/authors/120000004519"},"ban_comment":false,"channels":["global-channel","a-stock-channel","xgb-channel","us-stock-channel"],"comment_count":0,"content":"<p>纳指盘初涨0.89%，标普500指数涨0.74%，道指涨0.59%；苹果新品发布会进入倒计时，盘初跌0.14%；特斯拉涨超2%；英伟达涨超2%；戴尔盘初涨逾5%，该公司将加入标普500指数；波音盘初涨超2%，因其与工会达成初步劳资协议；汇丰控股盘初涨逾2%，报道称汇丰考虑合并商业银行和投资银行，以降低成本。阿里巴巴盘初跌0.38%，阿里巴巴正式纳入港股通，于9月10日生效。热门中概股多数下跌，蔚来跌超3%，微博、有道跌超2%，哔哩哔哩、贝壳、京东、腾讯音乐等跌超1%。</p>\n","content_more":"","content_text":"纳指盘初涨0.89%，标普500指数涨0.74%，道指涨0.59%；苹果新品发布会进入倒计时，盘初跌0.14%；特斯拉涨超2%；英伟达涨超2%；戴尔盘初涨逾5%，该公司将加入标普500指数；波音盘初涨超2%，因其与工会达成初步劳资协议；汇丰控股盘初涨逾2%，报道称汇丰考虑合并商业银行和投资银行，以降低成本。阿里巴巴盘初跌0.38%，阿里巴巴正式纳入港股通，于9月10日生效。热门中概股多数下跌，蔚来跌超3%，微博、有道跌超2%，哔哩哔哩、贝壳、京东、腾讯音乐等跌超1%。","cover_images":[],"display_time":1725888766,"fund_codes":[],"global_channel_name":"7x24快讯","global_more_uri":"wscn://wallstreetcn.com/live","has_live_reading":false,"highlight_title":"","id":2784286,"images":[],"is_calendar":false,"is_favourite":false,"is_priced":false,"is_scaling":false,"reference":"","related_themes":[],"score":2,"symbols":[],"tags":[],"title":"美股盘初：三大股指集体走高，特斯拉涨超2%","type":"live","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/livenews/2784286"},{"article":null,"author":{"avatar":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/bc3971d4-2d62-4d54-b1dd-7058c60c6ffa","display_name":"罗俊","id":694840,"is_followed":false,"uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/authors/694840"},"ban_comment":false,"channels":["us-stock-channel","global-channel"],"comment_count":0,"content":"<p>纳斯达克综合指数日内涨幅达1.0%，报16858.44点。</p>\n\n<p>恐慌指数VIX波动率日内跌幅达7.0%，报20.80；标普500指数目前涨0.86%。</p>\n","content_more":"","content_text":"纳斯达克综合指数日内涨幅达1.0%，报16858.44点。\n\n恐慌指数VIX波动率日内跌幅达7.0%，报20.80；标普500指数目前涨0.86%。","cover_images":[],"display_time":1725888765,"fund_codes":[],"global_channel_name":"7x24快讯","global_more_uri":"wscn://wallstreetcn.com/live","has_live_reading":false,"highlight_title":"","id":2784287,"images":[],"is_calendar":false,"is_favourite":false,"is_priced":false,"is_scaling":false,"reference":"","related_themes":[],"score":1,"symbols":[],"tags":[],"title":"","type":"live","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/livenews/2784287"},{"article":null,"author":{"avatar":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/ivanka_avatar_5.png","display_name":"葛冬瑾","id":120000004519,"is_followed":false,"uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/authors/120000004519"},"ban_comment":false,"channels":["global-channel","forex-channel"],"comment_count":0,"content":"<p>据<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ci3PksYpgARYBg93VFOtQw\" rel=\"nofollow\">上海发布</a>，市委书记陈吉宁今天（9月9日）下午会见了德国科隆市市长何珂一行。陈吉宁说，上海同科隆等德国城市交流交往密切，希望进一步加强沟通对接，发挥各自优势，把握城市数字化智能化绿色化发展机遇，围绕企业转型升级、绿色低碳发展、城市精细管理、人工智能治理、老年专业照护等领域深化交流互鉴、推动项目落地、打造合作样板，积极拓展人文交流新渠道新载体，切实加强两国地方特别是青少年之间的友好交流交往，更好播下相知相近、和睦相处的种子，为中德关系取得更大发展作出地方的积极贡献。</p>\n","content_more":"<p>何珂表示，上海这座城市的活力和创新极具吸引力，在数字化绿色化转型和城市治理等方面走在了前列。深化城市间的务实合作，推动教育、文化等领域人文交流，对双方都至关重要。希望持续加强经贸往来，围绕产业转型、绿色发展、城市管理、教育合作、老年照护等方面共享经验智慧，更好增进友谊、实现共赢发展。</p>\n","content_text":"据上海发布，市委书记陈吉宁今天（9月9日）下午会见了德国科隆市市长何珂一行。陈吉宁说，上海同科隆等德国城市交流交往密切，希望进一步加强沟通对接，发挥各自优势，把握城市数字化智能化绿色化发展机遇，围绕企业转型升级、绿色低碳发展、城市精细管理、人工智能治理、老年专业照护等领域深化交流互鉴、推动项目落地、打造合作样板，积极拓展人文交流新渠道新载体，切实加强两国地方特别是青少年之间的友好交流交往，更好播下相知相近、和睦相处的种子，为中德关系取得更大发展作出地方的积极贡献。","cover_images":[],"display_time":1725887651,"fund_codes":[],"global_channel_name":"7x24快讯","global_more_uri":"wscn://wallstreetcn.com/live","has_live_reading":false,"highlight_title":"","id":2784284,"images":[],"is_calendar":false,"is_favourite":false,"is_priced":false,"is_scaling":false,"reference":"","related_themes":[],"score":1,"symbols":[],"tags":[],"title":"上海市委书记陈吉宁会见德国科隆市市长何珂","type":"live","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/livenews/2784284"},{"article":null,"author":{"avatar":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/ivanka_avatar_5.png","display_name":"葛冬瑾","id":120000004519,"is_followed":false,"uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/authors/120000004519"},"ban_comment":false,"channels":["global-channel","bond-channel"],"comment_count":0,"content":"<p>为贯彻落实党的二十届三中全会关于深化国资国企改革、强化人大国有资产管理监督的部署安排，加大企业国有资产法的贯彻实施力度，全国人大常委会9日启动企业国有资产法执法检查。</p>\n\n<p>执法检查中，检查组将重点检查8方面内容：企业国有资产经营管理和改革发展总体情况；出资人职责履行情况；国家出资企业公司治理情况；企业国有资产基础管理情况；国有资产监督情况；与法律配套的行政法规、部门规章以及地方性法规的制定情况；法律实施中存在的其他问题，对推进法律实施的意见和建议；对企业国有资产法修改的意见和建议。（新华社）</p>\n","content_more":"","content_text":"为贯彻落实党的二十届三中全会关于深化国资国企改革、强化人大国有资产管理监督的部署安排，加大企业国有资产法的贯彻实施力度，全国人大常委会9日启动企业国有资产法执法检查。\n\n执法检查中，检查组将重点检查8方面内容：企业国有资产经营管理和改革发展总体情况；出资人职责履行情况；国家出资企业公司治理情况；企业国有资产基础管理情况；国有资产监督情况；与法律配套的行政法规、部门规章以及地方性法规的制定情况；法律实施中存在的其他问题，对推进法律实施的意见和建议；对企业国有资产法修改的意见和建议。（新华社）","cover_images":[],"display_time":1725886895,"fund_codes":[],"global_channel_name":"7x24快讯","global_more_uri":"wscn://wallstreetcn.com/live","has_live_reading":false,"highlight_title":"","id":2784282,"images":[],"is_calendar":false,"is_favourite":false,"is_priced":false,"is_scaling":false,"reference":"","related_themes":[],"score":1,"symbols":[],"tags":[],"title":"全国人大常委会启动企业国有资产法执法检查","type":"live","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/livenews/2784282"}],"next_cursor":"1725886895","op_cursor":"10943568","polling_cursor":"2784310"}